# tooling

- use `uv` package manager
- use `uv run ruff` for all linting and formatting
- use `uv run pytest` for running unit tests

# guidelines

- when editing code, check for unit test coverage and add or edit relevant unit tests

# playground rules

- do not edit dependencies directly in `pyproject.toml`, use package manager
- do not lint and format code directly, use tools
